{"tid":2505874,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生被控管有雷射筆 鄭紀航裁定罪名不成立","createTime":"2021-04-27T03:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T03:34:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8fb6732ea95cfee2e34f4d4fefe4119cc5e0f8","tid":2505874,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:03:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15280&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6zDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=3e602f0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15280</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#鄭紀航裁判官 #續審 (4/3) #裁決<br />\n👤盧 #1108香港仔  <br />\n<br />\n控罪: 在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月8日，在香港仔海旁道近香港仔海濱公園的公眾地方，無合法權限或合理辯解而攜有攻擊性武器，即一個能發出雷射光束的裝置。#雷射筆<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n鄭官表示已閱畢控辯雙方的書面陳詞並可以今日作出口頭裁決，辯方沒有反對。<br />\n<br />\n以下是裁決結果：<br />\n🥳罪名不成立🥳<br />\n<br />\n主要原因：<br />\n警方在處理雷射筆（即證物鏈) 上出現重大缺失，因此法庭對證物鏈有懷疑，例如：<br />\n-重要時間沒有紀錄<br />\n-沒有紀錄雷射筆是一直鎖在櫃桶"},{"pid":"a1e85b48dcf45e6b4cce1b67c37ae244da623bab","tid":2505874,"uid":134087,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:05:07.000Z","msg":"竟然<br />\n係咪佢第一單社運判不成立"},{"pid":"33a75f7485fc8b3984ee73ca9978c1757f759059","tid":2505874,"uid":50386,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:05:13.000Z","msg":"鄭紀航都不成立<br />\n證明呢單真係好離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882d8b3dffd9df3d46517629d538df3a96248ff4","tid":2505874,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d763c61f36c66c2dc508b8311151368e6b616d0c","tid":2505874,"uid":160592,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:05:28.000Z","msg"